localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_INTRO_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
Hi, I'm #0#! I'm here to show you how to manage your Empire.

Let's get started!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_AYTO_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
This is your Town Hall. It will let you train villagers.

To select the Town Hall, click on it.

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_ALDEANO_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
The bottom panel will show the available actions.

Click on the villager button to begin training a villager.

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_SELECCIONAR_ALDEANO_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
Well done! You have trained a villager.

Select it using the mouse!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_MOVER_ALDEANO_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
When you select a unit, you can move it by clicking on the desired place of the map.

Try it, click on the selected area!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_ARBOL_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
Villagers perform collecting tasks!

Click on a tree to cut it!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_ESPERA_LECCION
localization_strings.text: It will only take a few seconds... :)

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_RECOLECCION_LECCION
localization_strings.text: When the cutting has finished, click on the resource to pick up the wood.

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_CONSTRUIR_LECCION
localization_strings.text: Well done! Now I will show you how to create buildings. First, click the BUILD button.

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_CASA_LECCION
localization_strings.text: The next step is to select the desired building. Choose "House I".

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_COLOCAR_LECCION
localization_strings.text: Now click on the terrain to choose the placement of the house. The construction will begin!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_CABALLERO_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
Well done! You are ready for your first battle.

Click on this knight to select it!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_ATACAR_LECCION
localization_strings.text:
Trolls are your enemies! Defeat them or they will eliminate you!

Click on the troll to attack him!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_BATALLA_LECCION
localization_strings.text: The units are attacking each other right now. The bars over them show their life. Don't worry, they are just weak trolls!

localization_strings.name: TUTORIAL_ENHORABUENA_LECCION
localization_strings.text: Very good! Now you're ready to build the biggest Social Empire on Facebook! Good luck!!

localization_strings.text: AWESOME! You regained control of your wells again an could put off the fire on the fields and mill!

localization_strings.text: VERY WELL! You defeated the trolls and regained control of the stone mines!

localization_strings.name: POPUP_MISION_CAMPAMENTO_PIE_ALIADOS_END
localization_strings.text: BRILLIANT! You rescued your allies and they will help you to fight against the trolls now!

localization_strings.text: YOU DID IT! You saved the animals and now they are free again!

localization_strings.name: POPUP_MISION_CAMPAMENTO_PIE_ASEDIO_END

localization_strings.text: The statues hid treacherous skeletons and you defeat them all!

localization_strings.text: Help the egiptians to retrieve the Gems of Power and prevent evil Anubis Priests from reviving his deceased Paraoh.

localization_strings.name: POPUP_MISION_ELFOSARBOL_FOOTER_END
localization_strings.text: WELL DONE! You restored the Natural Balance on the woods. 2 Archer Elfs join your ranks as proof of gratitude!

localization_strings.text: ¡LET'S FREE THE ENT FROM THE DEVIL SPELL!

localization_strings.text: WE'LL HELP YOU TO DEFEAT BALROG!

localization_strings.name: POPUP_DRAGON_TAMING_HELP
localization_strings.text:
- HOW TO RIDE A DRAGON


1. Once you have got your rider in the Rider Academy, select it and put it in the Dragon Riding.

 2. Add your dragon to the Dragon Riding so the Rider can ride it!

3. Remember that the Rider and Dragon must be compatible so the riding can be successfully completed (check the Rider Academy for more details).

4. Once you have both Rider and Dragon in the building, press the 'Ride the Dragon' button to get your super powerful new unit!

localization_strings.name: POPUP_RIDER_TRAINING_HELP_SELECT
localization_strings.text:
- HOW TO TRAIN A DRAGON RIDER

1. Select the Rider you like (warning: put the mouse over a Rider and you'll see the dragons he can ride below!)

2. You must demonstrate you are worthy of riding a dragon: complete all the adventures and reach the END! (each time you complete an adventure, your progress bar on top will fill out)

 3- You must wait some time before playing again (you also have a button to recover yourself quicker!)

4. When you complete the last adventure, press the Get Rider button to get your Dragon Rider!

5. Once you get your Rider, take it to the Dragon Riding Building! (check the Store)

missions.title: Train villager
missions.description: You need villagers to collect resources. Click on your Town Hall and then on the TRAIN button at the bottom panel.

missions.title: Send villager to farm land
missions.description: Your farm land needs villagers to produce food. First click on a villager and then click on the farm land.

missions.title: Collect food
missions.description: When the food is ready to be collected an icon appears. Click on it to get the resources!

missions.title: Cut trees and get wood
missions.description: You got food, but you'll also need wood. Click on a villager and the click again on a tree. The villager will automatically cut all surrounding trees!

missions.title: Move mouse wheel to zoom
missions.description: Rotate the mouse wheel or click and drag the slider at the lower right of the screen to zoom in/out. It will help you to spot buildings or units!

missions.title: Build another farm land
missions.description: Farm lands are essential to increase your empire because they provide you with food. Go to BUILD > Buildings > Resources and place another farm land.

missions.title: Build another house
missions.description: Villagers and warriors live in houses! The more houses you build, the more units you can train. Go to BUILD > Buildings > Houses and place a House I.

missions.title: Build barracks
missions.description: You'll need an army for coming battles! Click on the 'Build' button, select the 'Attack' category and finally click on the Barracks I building.

missions.title: Train 3 Spearmen
missions.description: Start building your army with some spearmen. Click on the barracks building, and then click on the TRAIN button at the lower interface. Repeat this 3 times.

missions.title: Train 2 villagers
missions.description: Click on the Town Hall and then on the Train button at the lower interface. Do this twice to train two villagers.

missions.title: Build mill
missions.description: Mills will provide you with food, like farm lands. Go to BUILD > Buildings > Resources to build a mill.

missions.title: Send villager to mill
missions.description: Mills don't work alone! They need villagers. Select a villager and click on the mill to put him in.

missions.title: Select food on mill
missions.description: Choose one of the options to start producing the quantity of food you want!

missions.title: Put another villager on mill
missions.description: Increase your food outcome adding another villager to your mill! (if you don't have any villagers available, you can train them at your Town Hall)

missions.title: Get villager out of mill
missions.description: If you don't have resources to train villagers, you can get them out your buildings. Click on your mill and then click on a villager portrait at the lower interface to get it out of your mill.

missions.title: Extract 3 Gold
missions.description: Gold will make you more powerful! It is used to train the best units. Select a villager and click on a gold vein  (Explore the map to find gold veins)

missions.title: Select with double click
missions.description: Double click 1 spearman to select the 3 at one, and move them near your Town Hall fountain. Double-clicking is very useful!

missions.title: Kill 3 trolls
missions.description: Click on the Square Tool at the lower right of interface, and click and drag to select your units. (You can also use <SPACE>, it's easier and faster!). Then attack 3 trolls.

missions.title: Build sheep ranch
missions.description: Sheeps are funny... and tasty! But they need a sheep ranch! Build one going to BUILD > Buildings > Resources. It will provide you with some food!

missions.title: Capture sheep
missions.description: Ok! If you already got a sheep ranch, now go for some sheeps. Select a villager and click on a sheep to capture it.

missions.title: Send sheep to ranch
missions.description: If you already captured a sheep with a villager, select the sheep and send it to the ranch!

missions.title: Collect sheep ranch
missions.description: When a sheep ranch is ready to collect (you will see a food icon), click on it!

missions.title: Build 3 more farm lands
missions.description: Build 3 more farm lands to feed your soldiers! Remember you can train villagers at your Town Hall and then direct them towards your farms to produce more food simultaneously.

missions.title: Collect 5 farm lands
missions.description: Collect 5 farm lands. Important: Farm lands needs wood to be rebuilded, try to have always some on your inventory (see stats at the upper left of the screen).

missions.title: Build 4 more houses
missions.description: Build 4 more houses to increase your population limit. (BUILD > Buildings > Houses)

missions.title: Build gold mine
missions.description: Gold can also be obtained from gold mines, buy you can only own one. Go to Buildings > Resources and build it now!

missions.title: Put villager on gold mine
missions.description: Gold mines need villagers to extract the gold. Bring one of them to the mine (if you don't have any villager available, remember to create them at your Town Hall).

missions.title: Build Archery
missions.description: An archery will allow you to train archer infantry. Archers have a longer range than normal infantry. You can find the Archery in the Attack section of the BUILD menu.

missions.title: Train 3 Light Archers
missions.description: Train 3 light archers at your archery! Remember, click the archery an then click the train button at the bottom.

missions.title: Kill 5 more trolls
missions.description: It's time to kill trolls! Select your units with the SQUARE TOOL at the bottom right OR directly with a double click. Then click on an evil troll to attack him!

missions.title: Build 5 decorations
missions.description: It's not all about battling! Put some decorations to your empire to make it more beautiful! Go to BUILD > Decorations and place 5 of them.

missions.title: Put name to empire
missions.description: Every empire has a name! Put a name to yours too! Click at your empire name at the top right corner.

missions.title: Cut 10 trees
missions.description: Click on a villager and click on a tree to cut it. If the tree is near a group of trees, the villager will cut them all automatically!

missions.title: Collect 10 stones
missions.description: Stone is very important to build your defensive structures! Use your villagers to collect 10 stone!

missions.title: Build 2 towers near Town Hall
missions.description: Build 2 towers near your Town Hall to protect it from your enemies. It's your most important building! (BUILD > Defense)

missions.title: Build wall
missions.description: Build a row of 20 Wall I in the lower left border of your empire to start creating a defensive wall! Go to BUILD > Defense > Walls.

missions.title: Move wall
missions.description: Choose a Wall I and then Move it with the Move option on the interface (directional cross icon).

missions.title: Build stables I
missions.description: Your army needs cavalry! Build an stable to train light knights. (BUILD > Attack)

missions.title: Train 3 Light Knights
missions.description: You'll need more warriors before facing your first real battle! Train 3 light knights at your new Stables I!

missions.title: Select unit with Square Tool
missions.description: Choose multiple units with the Square Tool at the lower right of the interface (you can also use the <SPACE> bar, is much faster!)

missions.title: Kill all trolls
missions.description: Kill all trolls in your empire! You can check how many of them are left on the counter at the lower right of the screen. Try to destroy their towers first!

missions.title: Rescue Princess!
missions.description: When you finish with all the trolls, free the Princess and get the treasure!

missions.title: Visit #0#!
missions.description: Click on the portrait of #0# on the lower interface and see how beautiful an empire can look like!

missions.title: Build lumber mill / Put peasant
missions.description: Build a lumber mill and put a villager in to start producing wood! (You can find it at BUILD > Buildings > Resources).

missions.title: Select wood option
missions.description: Choose one of the options to start producing the quantity of wood you want!

missions.title: Put another villager on lumber mill
missions.description: Increase your wood outcome adding another villager to your lumber mill! (if you don't have available villagers on your map, remember you can train them on your Town Hall)

missions.title: Build cow ranch
missions.description: Build a cow ranch to hold your cows. (BUILD > Buildings > Resources)

missions.title: Put cow on ranch
missions.description: Bring a cow into the cow ranch to start producing some food.

missions.title: Build Market
missions.description: Build a Market to buy and sell resources! (Market is at BUILD > Buildings > Miscellaneous)

missions.title: Recruit Friend Market
missions.description: Recruit a friend to help you on the opening of your fabulous Market!

missions.title: Spend 1 cash
missions.description: Cash is useful to buy units, buildings, friends for social buildings, etc. Make yourself a gift and spend 1 cash in what you wish!

missions.title: Open Market
missions.description: Once you have filled up your Market with friends, click on the Open building to open it and be able to use it!

missions.title: Check collections
missions.description: Click on the gift icon at the lower right of the screen, then click on the Trophy icon. If you complete these collections you can get unique warriors and items!

missions.title: Get Daily Bonus 3 days
missions.description: Play 3 days in a row and click on the Daily Bonus bag at the left of the screen to get extra gold!

missions.title: Reach 40 population
missions.description: Reach 40 of population. It will be a sign of your empire expansion!

missions.title: Harvest 10 Gold veins
missions.description: Get 10 gold veins to increase your resource account, soon you'll need to use it!

missions.title: Build Stone Mine I
missions.description: Stone is very necessary to build defensive buildings. Build a Stone Mine to start producing this needful resource! (BUILD > Buildings > Resources)

missions.title: Attack 1 player
missions.description: Attacking other players provides much gold and xp! Click on the WORLD icon (blue) at the top, then click on the Attack button of a player. Read the Battle Help before starting!

missions.title: Defensive Strategy
missions.description: Click on the WORLD button (blue icon on top right) and then click on the OPTIONS button at the top of the screen. Select the 'My defensive strategy' button and choose your units behavior.

missions.title: Collect mill
missions.description: Pick up the food your mill produced to feed your troops!

missions.title: Collect lumber mill
missions.description: Pick up the wood your lumber mill produced to keep building stuff!

missions.title: Collect stone mine
missions.description: Pick up the stone your stone mine produced to keep building more defensive structures!

missions.title: Collect gold mine
missions.description: Pick up the gold your gold mine produced to keep building more defensive structures!

missions.title: Get 200 stone in Market
missions.description: Get 200 stone units in the Market. Click on the Market building, then click on the Visit Market at the lower interface. Then click twice on the BUY button of the stone icon.

missions.title: Get 100 wood in Market
missions.description: Get 100 wood units in the Market. Click on the Market building, then click on the Visit Market at the lower interface. Then click twice on the BUY button of the wood icon.

missions.title: Attack 1 friend!
missions.description: Click on the WORLD word in one of your friends portrait (if you can't see it, first click on the Assist word and come back to your empire) and attack him. For once he'll forgive you! =P

missions.title: Check Attacks
missions.description: Click on the WORLD button (blue) and then click on the BATTLE RESULTS button at the top of the screen. Then check your attacks and who attacked you!

missions.title: Build house II
missions.description: Houses II allow you to put in more people! Build one or update a House I clicking on one and using the UPGRADE option at the lower interface.

missions.title: Store decoration
missions.description: Click on a decoration and then click again on the STORE icon at the lower interface. You can retrieve your decoration (or sell it) clicking on BUILD > Storage.

missions.title: Build/Open Eagles I
missions.description: Eagles allow you to spy your enemy before attacking him! Build one and hire friends to open it! (BUILD > Buildings > Miscellaneous)

missions.title: Sell 100 wood
missions.description: Sell 100 wood units in the Market. Click on the Sell button to get gold in exchange!

missions.title: Expand 2 Acres
missions.description: Click on a FOR SALE post on your empire to buy land and continue your expansion!

missions.title: Build Workshop I
missions.description: Build a workshop I to build rams and be able to destroy doors of enemies' fortifications (BUILD > Attack).

missions.title: Free 3 archers
missions.description: Free the 3 archers kidnapped by trolls! (daily mission)

missions.title: Kill 5 Devious trolls
missions.description: Kill 5 Devious Trolls. They are implied in the complot to destroy your empire!

missions.title: Coordinated Attack
missions.description: Send 5 archers to attack the same tower, and afterwards send your melee units against the same tower!

missions.title: Use Eagle
missions.description: Click on the world icon at the upper part and then on the SPY button on any player to spy his empire!

missions.title: Defeat two players
missions.description: Defeat two players (including your friends!) to get gold... and glory!

missions.title: Build Harbor
missions.description: Build a Harbor (Buildings > Miscellaneous), invite your friends and click on the OPEN button to explore the seas!

missions.title: Check the map
missions.description: Once your Harbor is open, click on it and then press the Let's Sail button to see the map!

missions.title: Complete Mysterious Isle on 1 star
missions.description: Use the Harbor to travel to Mysterious Isle and retrieve the treasure that the trolls stole to your ancestors! Complete Mysterious Island (1 star).

missions.title: Upgrade Barracks II
missions.description: Upgrade your Barracks II to train stronger units! (Buildings > Attack or UPGRADE button in Barracks I interface)

missions.title: Train 3 Swordsmen
missions.description: Train 3 Swordsmen in your Barracks II... you'll need them soon!

missions.title: Sail in another way
missions.description: Access the map in another way: click on the world icon on top and then click on the ship surrounding the island.

missions.title: Complete Unknown Isle (1 star)
missions.description: Unknown Isle is a cold, hostile place, but in the loot that the Ravager Trolls protect lies hidden a nice amount of gold! Complete Unknown Isle (1 star).

missions.title: Build 2 tower II
missions.description: Build two Tower II in your empire. You will get rid of enemies faster! (BUILD > Defense)

missions.title: Build 20 Wall II
missions.description: Build 20 Wall II in the lower left row of your 1st acre  (BUILD > Defense). You can also upgrade the Wall I you already have if you click on one wall and then click UPGRADE on the lower interface.

missions.title: Build 2 Pumpkin Crop
missions.description: Build 2 Pumpkin Crop to obtain more food.

missions.title: Invoke allies
missions.description: Build an Allies Building and get 9 allies to open it!

missions.title: Upgrade to Archery II
missions.description: Upgrade you Archery to train better archers! (Buildings > Attack)

missions.title: Rescue Kidnapped Soldiers
missions.description: The trolls have kidnapped some soldiers! Free them! (daily mission)

missions.title: Defeat 3 players
missions.description: Prove yourself and defeat 3 players... including your friends!

missions.title: Build Mill II
missions.description: Build the Mill II to increase food production.

missions.title: Recruit 6 friends for Mill II
missions.description: Recruit 6 friends to open the mill.

missions.title: Hire all villagers in Mill II
missions.description: Hire all villagers in your new mill to take full advantage of it!

missions.title: 8 hours Mill
missions.description: Leave the mill collecting for 8 hours.

missions.title: Upgrade Market
missions.description: Upgrade your Market to Market II to buy or sell more resources.

missions.title: Build 8 towers
missions.description: Build 8 towers in your empire... the trolls will attack soon and you must protect yourself!

missions.title: Extinguish fire
missions.description: If the trolls set fire to buildings of your empire, click on a villager and then click again on the fire to extinguish it!

missions.title: Help a friend
missions.description: Visit a friend and help him to collect as many resources as you can!

missions.title: Build Prize Building
missions.description: Build a Prize building and get allies to obtain fabulous special units! (Buildings > Miscellaneous)

missions.title: Get recruitment prize
missions.description: Tell 3 friends to help you get a fantastic special unit on your Prize Building!

missions.title: Build Traning Stables
missions.description: Build the Training Stables to improve the mobility of your units!

missions.title: Capture a horse and...
missions.description: Capture a horse with a villager or warrior and take it to the Training Stables.

missions.title: Lead Swordsman to Stables...
missions.description: Once you have put a horse, lead a Swordsman to the Training Stables to turn him into a medium knight!

missions.title: Complete Mysterious Isle (2 stars)
missions.description: Complete Mysterious Isle on 2 stars to obtain much more gold and XP!

missions.title: Upgrade Town Hall
missions.description: Upgrade your Town Hall. Select it and click on UPGRADE at the bottom part of the interface.

missions.title: Train 2 villagers
missions.description: Train 2 villagers in your new Town Hall. Now they will run as fast as a hare!

missions.title: Upgrade Stables
missions.description: Upgrade Stables to Stables II to train heavier mounted units!

missions.title: Train 3 Medium Knights
missions.description: Train 3 Medium Knights... You're getting stronger every day!

missions.title: Get Treasure Chest!
missions.description: Get the Treasure Chest, defended by the trolls! (Daily mission)

missions.title: Build Allies Market
missions.description: Build the Allies Market so your friends can send you free resources! (Buildings > Miscellaneous)

missions.title: Get wood Allies Market
missions.description: Tell your friends to help you and get at least 500 units of wood in the allies market!

missions.title: Undiscovered Isle (1 star)
missions.description: Discover the secrets of the Undiscovered Isle (1 star). Beware of the evil skeletons!

missions.title: Build Gold Mine II
missions.description: The more gold the better! Build a Gold Mine II to increase the production.

missions.title: Put 4 villagers in Gold Mine II
missions.description: Take the most out of the Gold Mine II adding 4 villagers to it.

missions.title: Build Treasure Mine
missions.description: Need help to complete the collections? Build a Treasure Mine to get one item EACH DAY!

missions.title: Collect object in Treasure Mine
missions.description: Collect the surprise item in the Treasure Mine (lapse of 24h. since the last picked up gift).

missions.title: Build Workshop II
missions.description: Build a Workshop II to enjoy a high damage weapon: ¡scorpions! (BUILD > Attack)

missions.title: Open Workshop II
missions.description: Tell your friends to help you open the Workshop II... scorpions wreak havoc against enemy towers!

missions.title: Build 3 Scorpions
missions.description: Build 3 scorpions in the Workshop II and get ready for the last stage of the process!

missions.title: Destroy 1 tower with Scorpions
missions.description: When the next troll camp appears, destroy one tower with a group of 3 Scorpions... notice that weak enemy towers don't have enough range to destroy your scorpions!

missions.title: Build Tower III
missions.description: Build a Tower III to protect yourself better against incoming attacks!

missions.title: Build Altar of Heroes
missions.description: Build an Altar of Heroes to purchase powerful special units!

missions.title: Get a hero
missions.description: Get a hero in the Altar of Heroes to help you defeat your enemies more easily! (Click on the GET HERO button)

missions.title: Kill Axethrower
missions.description: Kill an Axethrower. These depictable beings won't hesitate to kill your units from the distance!

missions.title: Rescue villagers
missions.description: Rescue the villagers captured by trolls! They would do the same for you! (daily mission)

missions.title: Put a hero on your map
missions.description: Play 5 days in a row and get your special unit. To put your hero on the map, go to BUILD > STORAGE.

missions.title: Save the penguins!
missions.description: Go to Arctic Isle (1 star) and save the penguins... Beware, a big beast is waiting for you!

missions.title: Fight against two player from your same level
missions.description: Fight against two players from your same level and show up your skills! you don't need to win, but must finish the combat!

missions.title: Build Lumber Mill II
missions.description: Build a Lumber Mill II to produce more wood!

missions.title: Put 4 villager into Lumber Mill II
missions.description: Put 4 villagers into the Lumber Mill II to increase its production outcome!

missions.title: Build Small Refuge
missions.description: Build a Small Refuge and before logging out put in 2 of your most valuable units so other players don't destroy them!

missions.title: Build Big Church
missions.description: Invoke heavenly powers and build a Big Church to raise your population limit. (BUILD > Wonders)

missions.title: More Ravager Trolls!
missions.description: Trolls hid more treasures yet, and this time they have doubled its number to protect it! Complete Unknown Isle on 2 stars!

missions.title: Build Barracks III
missions.description: Build a Barracks III to train the renowned Long Swordsman!

missions.title: Train 3 Long Swordsman
missions.description: Train 3 Long Swordsman, they will help you defeat your enemies more quickly!

missions.title: Upgrade to Eagles II
missions.description: Upgrade to Eagles II so your eagles have more life and can explore more enemy terrain!

missions.title: Build Heroes Grave
missions.description: Build a Heroes Grave to have the chance of resurrecting your lost special units!

missions.title: Liberate Prisoner Troll
missions.description: Liberate the Prisoner Troll. He never bent his knee against the evil behavior of his tribe and has always tried to be a good troll!

missions.title: Kill 1 Boar Rider
missions.description: Kill 1 Boar Rider! This mounted beast won't dare to kill your fighters when you are not watching!

missions.title: Thrice Trolls!
missions.description: Complete Mysterious Isle on 3 stars and defeat all the evil trolls!

missions.title: Build Stone Mine II
missions.description: Build a Stone Mine II to keep producing more stone for the welfare of your Empire!

missions.title: Build 20 Wall III
missions.description: Build 20 Wall III in the bottom left row or upgrade your current walls there. This way your enemies will have a hard time trying to put their foot on your empire!

missions.title: Build Cow Ranch II
missions.description: Build Cow Ranch II… if the meat is tasty now, it will be tastier with this improvement!

missions.title: Lead a cow to ranch
missions.description: Lead a cow to the ranch to get a good portion of food!

missions.title: Build Round Table
missions.description: Build a Round Table so your allies can help you getting incredible bonuses!

missions.title: Put 4 allies to Round Table
missions.description: Recruit 4 allies to the Round Table to get the first prize!

missions.title: Destroy 2 Troll Towers III
missions.description: Destroy 2 Troll Towers III and let those ugly beasts know who rules this empire!!

missions.title: Rescue Prince Arthur!
missions.description: Prince Arthur has been kidnapped by evil trolls! Save him before it's too late!

missions.title: Build Archery II
missions.description: Build an Archery III to train lethal Heavy Archers!

missions.title: Train 3 heavy archers
missions.description: Train 3 heavy archers. You'll be more dreaded by your enemies!

missions.title: Build Temple
missions.description: Build a Temple to obtain more gold resources!

missions.title: Avenge Ancestors
missions.description: Trolls conquered this island and killed all its human dwellers. Avenge your ancestors and conquer Emergent Isle (1 star)!!

missions.title: Update House II
missions.description: Update 4 House I to House II to put more citizens in!

missions.title: Expand 3 acres
missions.description: Expand 3 acres

missions.title: Open Church
missions.description: Open a Church so you can train healers!

missions.title: Train 3 healers
missions.description: Train 3 healers so they can heal your units during the combat!

missions.title: Attack 2 player more level
missions.description: Attack 2 players of more level than yours and show them who's the best!

missions.title: Free the wells
missions.description: Trolls have cut the water supply! Kill them to retrieve control of the wells!

missions.title: Build Stable III
missions.description: Build a Stable III to be able to train the dreaded heavy knights!

missions.title: Save Healers
missions.description: Save the captive healers from trolls' hands! They will join your army afterwards!

missions.title: Complete Misty Isle on 1 star
missions.description: Visit Misty Isle (1 star) and destroy the Town Hall of your Viking enemies before they come to conquer your land!

missions.title: Complete Unknown Isle 3 stars
missions.description: Visit Unknown Isle (3 stars) and let Ravager Trolls know who has the power!

missions.title: Build 3 eggplant farms
missions.description: Build 3 eggplant farms to increase your food outcome!

missions.title: Build 1 wall door
missions.description: Build 1 wall door so your units can come in and out of your empire easily and securely!

missions.title: Build Academy
missions.description: Build an Academy (Buildings > Investigation) to train your villagers to go faster and pile up more resources to gather!

missions.title: Build workshop III
missions.description: Build a Workshop III to be able to build destructive catapults!

missions.title: Sacrifice unit
missions.description: Build a sacrifice altar and sacrifice a unit to get part of the resources back to your inventory.

missions.title: Free 4 stone mines!
missions.description: Free the 4 stone mines from trolls control! This resource is basic for your survival! (daily mission)

missions.title: Complete Undiscovered Isle 2 stars
missions.description: Visit the Undiscovered Isle (2 stars) and kill all the skeletons that have spawned to end with the undead menace!

missions.title: Build Mill III
missions.description: Build a Mill III to increase your food outcome even more!

missions.title: Build 2 Tower IV
missions.description: Build 2 Tower IV to destroy your enemies almost with no hassles!

missions.title: Open Cathedral
missions.description: Open a Cathedral to train hypnotist monks! They are very powerful!

missions.title: Convert enemy with a monk
missions.description: Convert an enemy using a monk. Afterwards you can control that enemy for your purposes!

missions.title: Build Nursery
missions.description: Build a Nursery to help animals to breed.

missions.title: Put 2 horses inside
missions.description: Put 2 horses inside and wait for getting your new horse! You can produce as many as you need!

missions.title: Complete Dune Isle on 1 star
missions.description: Visit Dune Isle (1 star) and destroy the Golden Hall where the treacherous Mummy lives. Take care with Anubis servants!

missions.title: Build Gold Mine III

missions.title: Build Workshop IV

missions.title: Build a Lumber Mill III

missions.title: Build 2 carrot farms

missions.title: Open a Stone Mine III

missions.title: Build Eagles III
missions.description: Build an Eagles III to breed stronger eagles!

missions.title: Explore the Skeleton Statue
missions.description: Explore the Skeleton Statue and discover its hidden secret! (daily mission)

missions.title: Build House IV
missions.description: Build a House IV to be able to put more population in.

missions.title: Open a Fire Workshop

missions.title: Build Minery Academy

missions.title: Open Mill IV

missions.title: Train 3 Knights

missions.title: Build a Blacksmith
missions.description: Build a Blacksmith so melee, ranged and mounted troops spend less resources to be trained! That's really good news!!

missions.title: Build 5 Towers IV
missions.description: Build 5 Towers IV to improve your empire defenses. Put them strategically and they will badly hurt your enemies, promised!

missions.title: Build 10 Walls V
missions.description: Build 10 Walls V on the lower left row of your empire to improve you defensive structures.

missions.title: Build a Weather Machine
missions.description: Build a Weather Machine to be able to change the landscape at your will! That's magic, baby!!

missions.title: Build 2 watermelon Farms
missions.description: Build 2 watermelon Farms to increase your food outcome. Eating fruit is very healthy, but you already know that!

missions.title: Update Town Hall IV
missions.description: Update the Town Hall IV. If your villagers were really fast, now they will almost fly!

missions.title: Build Lumber Mill IV
missions.description: Build a Lumber Mill IV to increase your wood outcome.

missions.title: Build the Tavern
missions.description: Build a Tavern and you'll increase your maximum population capacity by 10 units… people that go to the Tavern don't need any home to live in!

missions.title: Build Wizardry Academy!
